channel.title: Project insanity help
channel.description:
I have added everything i nede to my project insanity. fixed the zammy boss. added skill cape emots. and did other stuff... The only thing i cant do is add models I tried tutorials but i am so stuck i have all deltascape models and inits and idk how to config them Only models im added are a costom scim and kite for donators :) any help would be nice
It is a refactored client becuase there is no class 8 i know how to do it on delta im trying to get away form that so dont tell me the class 8 way ! THANKYOU COME AGAN !

item.title: Project insanity help
item.dc:creator: @pk_flavor1 pk flavor
item.description:
@pk_flavor1 wrote:

i’m a good project insanity coder to do it go into itemdef.java in ur “client” and put something in there such as
case 15001:
itemDef.actions = new String[5];
itemDef.actions[1] = “Wield”;
itemDef.femaleEquip1 = 51800;//female
itemDef.modelOffset1 = -5;
itemDef.modelOffset2 = 2;
itemDef.modelZoom = 1490;
itemDef.modelRotation2 = 1400;
itemDef.modelRotation1 = 148;
itemDef.maleEquip1 = 51800;
itemDef.modelID = 51799;
itemDef.name = “Staff of light”;
itemDef.description = “Humming with power.”.getBytes();
break;
but u must have model’s for it to work if u want the model’s go to regionpk.tk and click webclient at top and download the cache and go into the cache and look for the folder “raw” but that folder into ur cache and if u want the “itemdef.java” codes then replay to this.

                                                   -pk flavor
